1
00:00:24,210 --> 00:00:25,780
The special train will pass through

2
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:27,600
the tunnel where we're lying in wait
at 12:30.

3
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:28,670
Stay focused—

4
00:00:30,460 --> 00:00:32,840
we'll only have 20 seconds
to board the train.

5
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:33,340
Got it.

6
00:00:41,450 --> 00:00:44,230
[Mo Yungao's Special Train
from Guangchuan to Nanling]

7
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,450
What are you looking at?

8
00:02:02,180 --> 00:02:03,360
Nothing. Just rest.

9
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,660
After this trip,

10
00:02:06,710 --> 00:02:07,550
let's go get a drink.

11
00:02:07,550 --> 00:02:08,100
Sure.

12
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:55,050
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

13
00:03:55,470 --> 00:03:58,090
[Episode 21]

14
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:17,519
[Mo Yungao, Leader
of the Mo Faction Warlord of Beilian]

15
00:04:26,450 --> 00:04:27,930
You do enjoy

16
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:29,570
bringing me useless people

17
00:04:29,570 --> 00:04:31,500
to keep me entertained, don't you?

18
00:04:32,130 --> 00:04:33,390
You need to be patient.

19
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:38,740
Are you telling me what to do now?

20
00:04:38,930 --> 00:04:42,159
Do I look even a little impatient to you?

21
00:04:49,250 --> 00:04:50,390
What was that about?

22
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:52,240
Commander, didn't you just

23
00:04:52,890 --> 00:04:53,540
do this?

24
00:04:58,950 --> 00:04:59,920
I really

25
00:05:00,890 --> 00:05:02,690
was just trying to flick my hair.

26
00:05:02,990 --> 00:05:04,210
I... I'm sorry, Commander!

27
00:05:04,210 --> 00:05:05,040
Alright, alright.

28
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,570
Clean this up immediately.

29
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:14,680
Bai Yu.

30
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:17,790
Have you captured Zhang Haiqi yet?

31
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,360
Do you have any idea how much

32
00:05:27,870 --> 00:05:30,240
manpower and resources I spent
trying to avenge you?

33
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:32,440
If you really want to repay my kindness,

34
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,690
bring me a few more useful members
of the Zhang family.

35
00:05:35,690 --> 00:05:37,740
That would be worth far more
than anything else.

36
00:05:37,740 --> 00:05:38,470
Understood.

37
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:46,930
Report!

38
00:05:47,159 --> 00:05:47,980
Come in. Just come in.

39
00:05:47,980 --> 00:05:49,390
Stop knocking already.

40
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:54,250
Commander, when we passed through
the tunnel just now,

41
00:05:54,250 --> 00:05:55,500
someone tried to force her way
onto the train.

42
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,920
But she's highly skilled—

43
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,750
she actually managed to
evade a barrage of gunfire

44
00:05:58,750 --> 00:05:59,690
and suffered only minor injuries.

45
00:05:59,690 --> 00:06:01,860
Our men have captured her.

46
00:06:03,010 --> 00:06:06,560
Who would have the nerve to barge onto
my special train?

47
00:06:06,810 --> 00:06:08,830
We don't know her exact identity yet,

48
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:10,540
but while we were apprehending her,

49
00:06:10,540 --> 00:06:13,000
we also received a telegram
from Zhang Qishan.

50
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,310
It only said one thing—

51
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:17,240
that she's the person
you've been longing for, Commander.

52
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:17,860
A

53
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:19,720
woman surnamed Zhang.

54
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:21,780
Here's the telegram.

55
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:29,590
[Telegram Draft]

56
00:06:28,130 --> 00:06:29,040
This woman came to my residence

57
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,390
seeking a partnership.

58
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,420
She wanted evidence of your corruption
and abuse of power in Beilian.

59
00:06:32,420 --> 00:06:33,190
Out of consideration
for our years as colleagues,

60
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:34,320
I had no wish to involve myself
in this matter.

61
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:36,130
Furthermore, this woman bears
a Qilin tattoo on her body

62
00:06:36,130 --> 00:06:37,430
that only appears when her blood runs hot.

63
00:06:37,430 --> 00:06:39,500
I've heard that you've long searched for
such a person without success,

64
00:06:39,500 --> 00:06:41,870
so I deliberately revealed
your whereabouts to her

65
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:44,800
and leave her in your hands
to deal with as you see fit.

66
00:06:49,010 --> 00:06:49,670
Commander,

67
00:06:50,130 --> 00:06:51,130
what do you think?

68
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:53,190
Zhang Qishan?

69
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:55,810
He may act friendly towards me
on the surface,

70
00:06:55,810 --> 00:06:58,040
but he's stabbed me in the back
so many times.

71
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,240
This is just his way of

72
00:06:59,570 --> 00:07:02,430
clearing himself of suspicion—

73
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,780
worried I might think
he's one of the Zhang family.

74
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:07,510
Bring in that woman you caught.

75
00:07:07,740 --> 00:07:09,270
I want to see her for myself.

76
00:07:09,810 --> 00:07:10,740
Yes, Commander!

77
00:07:39,870 --> 00:07:41,310
What kind of life

78
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:43,159
am I living all day long?

79
00:08:13,930 --> 00:08:16,330
I was wondering
why you looked so familiar.

80
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:20,510
[File Name: Investigation Report on
the Southern Archives & the Zhang Family]

81
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:22,950
You're the Director of
the Southern Archives,

82
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:23,540
[Report]

83
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:25,080
Zhang Haiqi.

84
00:08:42,740 --> 00:08:44,510
The supreme god,

85
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:48,120
there is none who can compare to you.

86
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:51,020
We are mired in filth and insignificance,

87
00:08:51,020 --> 00:08:53,350
yet you still bestowed your favor upon me.

88
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:13,640
I've spent half my life
searching for your kind.

89
00:09:15,250 --> 00:09:18,580
Do you know how many people
from the Archives I've captured?

90
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:21,050
I found they were very different
from ordinary people.

91
00:09:21,050 --> 00:09:23,050
It was only after poring over countless
ancient texts

92
00:09:23,050 --> 00:09:24,510
that I finally understood

93
00:09:24,650 --> 00:09:25,840
that you belong to

94
00:09:26,290 --> 00:09:28,540
an ancient clan bearing the surname Zhang.

95
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:29,950
Within your clan,

96
00:09:29,970 --> 00:09:31,260
there's a legend:

97
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,650
every so often,

98
00:09:32,650 --> 00:09:35,390
a prodigy of the age is born—

99
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,400
one whose existence

100
00:09:37,420 --> 00:09:39,750
threatens the safety of your entire clan.

101
00:09:41,950 --> 00:09:43,370
Having seen you today,

102
00:09:43,390 --> 00:09:44,920
it seems the legend is true.

103
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:47,020
I'm deeply ashamed.

104
00:09:48,590 --> 00:09:50,520
There is no prodigy of this age.

105
00:09:51,010 --> 00:09:53,590
The fact that you pose a threat
to the Zhang family

106
00:09:53,590 --> 00:09:55,520
is the Zhang family's own problem.

107
00:09:59,630 --> 00:10:01,600
Let's move on to the next question:

108
00:10:01,890 --> 00:10:04,420
why did Zhang Qishan bring you

109
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,730
onto my train?

110
00:10:06,130 --> 00:10:07,330
What are you two up to?

111
00:10:11,250 --> 00:10:12,530
As for what Zhang Qishan is up to,

112
00:10:12,530 --> 00:10:13,840
you should ask him.

113
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:16,020
Scratching each other's backs—

114
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:19,670
I suppose there's some kind of deal
between you two.

115
00:10:19,670 --> 00:10:20,360
Indeed.

116
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,770
As expected of you.

117
00:10:25,070 --> 00:10:28,500
[Telegram Draft]

118
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:37,130
[Telegram Draft]

119
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:36,790
Send this

120
00:10:37,490 --> 00:10:38,880
to Zhang Qishan.

121
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:39,840
Yes, Commander.

122
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,550
If your goal has always been
to capture members of the Zhang family,

123
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:52,720
then you've already caught

124
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,240
me, a member of the Zhang family.

125
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:56,980
So can you call off the release
of the Twilight Grass?

126
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:58,460
Actually, I'm not interested in

127
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:00,440
capturing all of you Zhangs.

128
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:04,000
There's only one specific person
from the Zhang family

129
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:06,100
that I'm after.

130
00:11:08,530 --> 00:11:09,240
However,

131
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:12,700
since you're a member of the Zhang family,

132
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:14,070
you must know

133
00:11:14,090 --> 00:11:15,340
where that person is.

134
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:17,250
And you must

135
00:11:17,250 --> 00:11:18,620
have his file, too.

136
00:11:21,510 --> 00:11:24,170
It might even be sitting in your hands
right now.

137
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:26,790
I've already destroyed the Archives.

138
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:28,320
If you want to find his file,

139
00:11:28,860 --> 00:11:30,120
go dig for it yourself.

140
00:11:30,650 --> 00:11:31,370
However,

141
00:11:32,410 --> 00:11:34,610
I'm afraid you won't live until then.

142
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:36,040
That's impossible.

143
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:38,510
He'll definitely show himself eventually.

144
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:39,170
As

145
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:41,030
more and more of

146
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:42,480
you Zhangs disappear,

147
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:44,740
he'll realize

148
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:46,270
that he's the one I'm after.

149
00:11:46,570 --> 00:11:49,010
And when he does, he'll come to me
of his own accord.

150
00:11:49,010 --> 00:11:51,070
I have great respect for your people.

151
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:53,340
That's why I won't let
any part of you go to waste—

152
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:55,240
not a single one of you,

153
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,320
nor a single item

154
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:58,100
belonging to you.

155
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:11,130
Zhang Haiqi.

156
00:12:11,130 --> 00:12:13,930
Do you think it's possible
that this bodyguard...

157
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:17,020
It's his first time serving as
my bodyguard.

158
00:12:25,890 --> 00:12:27,090
You were responsible

159
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:29,810
for distracting me,

160
00:12:30,250 --> 00:12:30,910
while he

161
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:32,180
put on another face

162
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,940
and infiltrated my train as a bodyguard.

163
00:12:33,940 --> 00:12:37,990
As we speak, he's probably
looking for proof of my plans.

164
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:41,250
Once we're on the train,

165
00:12:41,250 --> 00:12:42,820
I'll deal with Mo Yungao,

166
00:12:42,820 --> 00:12:45,510
and you go find evidence of
his poisoning scheme.

167
00:12:45,510 --> 00:12:47,030
If there's any Twilight Grass
on the train,

168
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:48,050
destroy it all.

169
00:12:48,170 --> 00:12:50,410
We cannot allow even a single stalk
to enter Nanling.

170
00:12:50,410 --> 00:12:51,410
Darn it.

171
00:12:53,870 --> 00:12:55,170
Zhang Haitong?

172
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:57,500
Zhang Haiqing?

173
00:12:58,860 --> 00:13:00,000
Zhang Haijiang?

174
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:02,890
Zhang Haimu.

175
00:13:03,220 --> 00:13:04,290
Zhang Hairong.

176
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,650
Zhang Haiping.

177
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:11,390
Zhang Haicai.

178
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:13,650
They're all members of the Zhang family.

179
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,020
What are you doing?

180
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:28,840
This is not mine.

181
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,290
You remember that assassin

182
00:13:30,290 --> 00:13:31,490
named Bai Zhu, right?

183
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:39,670
I...

184
00:13:39,670 --> 00:13:41,530
I-I'm on my way to send a telegram.

185
00:13:43,430 --> 00:13:44,570
I want you.

186
00:13:45,050 --> 00:13:45,550
What?

187
00:13:50,650 --> 00:13:52,910
Well, the Commander is still waiting.

188
00:13:52,910 --> 00:13:54,750
How about we do it in a bit?

189
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,170
I want it now.

190
00:13:59,470 --> 00:14:00,120
No, no, no,

191
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:01,450
this is inappropriate.

192
00:14:04,030 --> 00:14:05,210
I-It hurts!

193
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:06,170
Ouch!

194
00:14:07,170 --> 00:14:08,430
I want your hand first.

195
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:09,820
[Zhang Haiqing] [Zhang Haijiang]

196
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:17,170
Ouch! It hurts!

197
00:14:17,170 --> 00:14:18,150
It really hurts!

198
00:14:55,450 --> 00:14:57,380
What the hell did you grow up eating

199
00:14:57,400 --> 00:14:58,430
to be so strong?

200
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:02,170
People like you.

201
00:15:06,110 --> 00:15:07,030
Liquor?

202
00:15:08,850 --> 00:15:12,050
You make medicinal liquor
with the Zhang family members?

203
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:14,080
It must be a great tonic, huh?

204
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:30,650
Trust

205
00:15:30,650 --> 00:15:31,890
is the greatest trap.

206
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:34,040
Whatever you place your trust in

207
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:36,480
is exactly what will lead to
your downfall.

208
00:15:37,170 --> 00:15:37,980
Miss,

209
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:38,750
look,

210
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:40,320
didn't we hook up before?

211
00:15:40,370 --> 00:15:41,790
On the Nan'an?

212
00:15:41,810 --> 00:15:42,700
I remember now.

213
00:15:42,700 --> 00:15:43,300
You are...

214
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,360
Bai Zhu, right?

215
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:45,220
You... You...

216
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:46,150
What did you say?

217
00:15:46,510 --> 00:15:48,580
One night together means something!

218
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:49,800
We may be enemies,

219
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,550
but I did let you leave that ship.

220
00:15:51,550 --> 00:15:53,500
You can't just turn your back on me
like that, right?

221
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:54,240
Bullshit!

222
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:56,790
Zhang Haiqi killed my sister.

223
00:15:56,790 --> 00:15:58,190
I'm going to kill you all.

224
00:15:58,250 --> 00:16:00,670
W-What are you talking about,

225
00:16:01,220 --> 00:16:02,230
Bai Zhu?

226
00:16:02,670 --> 00:16:04,100
I'm not Bai Zhu!

227
00:16:04,100 --> 00:16:05,770
Then who are you?

228
00:16:11,890 --> 00:16:12,550
Bai Yu!

229
00:16:20,550 --> 00:16:21,680
Is everything okay?

230
00:16:22,890 --> 00:16:23,820
Yeah, everything's okay.

231
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:25,050
I just knocked some things over,

232
00:16:25,050 --> 00:16:26,310
and I'm cleaning it up.

233
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,300
Lift your head.

234
00:16:40,220 --> 00:16:41,530
Are you guys...

235
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,290
Okay?

236
00:16:43,290 --> 00:16:44,350
How could we not be?

237
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:45,550
Go

238
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:48,920
and send this telegram to Zhang Qishan.

239
00:16:58,910 --> 00:16:59,970
Where's my sister?

240
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:01,700
You said she got off the ship.

241
00:17:05,150 --> 00:17:08,079
You're just locking the two of us up
in here like this?

242
00:17:08,550 --> 00:17:10,550
You do realize I could kill you right now,
don't you?

243
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:11,720
You're so beautiful,

244
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:13,349
yet your heart is so vicious.

245
00:17:13,750 --> 00:17:16,349
At least let me finish
this glass of wine first.

246
00:17:19,310 --> 00:17:22,109
The master of these snakes
is right next door,

247
00:17:22,660 --> 00:17:24,140
using his own way

248
00:17:25,180 --> 00:17:27,109
to manipulate them and protect me.

249
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,480
This is all Chen Xifeng's doing.

250
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:33,050
Bailejing really is a remarkable place.

251
00:17:34,050 --> 00:17:35,660
I've got quite a few talented

252
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:38,400
and extraordinary people
working under me now as well.

253
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:40,140
So you've known all along.

254
00:17:41,010 --> 00:17:42,110
This kind of snake

255
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:44,000
is known as the Fidelity Snake.

256
00:17:44,140 --> 00:17:46,250
It can tell friend from foe
and expose impostors.

257
00:17:46,250 --> 00:17:48,510
So in front of me, disguises are useless.

258
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:54,030
Now then,

259
00:17:55,250 --> 00:17:56,650
we'll wait for my men

260
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:58,240
to bring back that friend of yours—

261
00:17:58,240 --> 00:18:01,300
the one posing as a bodyguard
with that fake face of his.

262
00:18:01,350 --> 00:18:03,590
Then we'll talk about what happens next.

263
00:18:03,590 --> 00:18:05,170
Of course, you could always

264
00:18:05,380 --> 00:18:06,880
throw something at me right now

265
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:08,660
and punch a hole through my throat,

266
00:18:08,660 --> 00:18:11,060
just as that Salty Zhang once did.

267
00:18:11,380 --> 00:18:13,850
You should be faster than a snake.

268
00:18:14,380 --> 00:18:15,780
But bear with me for a bit.

269
00:18:20,790 --> 00:18:22,140
Beneath your sofa,

270
00:18:22,140 --> 00:18:24,430
I've placed one of my latest creations.

271
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:26,590
It's a special powder ground from

272
00:18:26,590 --> 00:18:29,250
the blossoms of the Twilight Grass.

273
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:32,850
I call it Yellow Jasmine.

274
00:18:33,270 --> 00:18:35,360
Do you have any idea how difficult it was

275
00:18:35,360 --> 00:18:37,060
to make the Twilight Grass bloom,

276
00:18:37,060 --> 00:18:39,590
and how many human lives it took
to feed them?

277
00:18:39,810 --> 00:18:40,660
This poison

278
